value:
It's so cozy here... I could sleep
anywhere. Inside...outside...

Peony is a friend of mine. She sings
me to sleep sometimes... She's very
kind, isn't she?

My tummy is grumbling... Once it's
full, then I'll really be ready for a nap.

Dökkálfar are scary, but...I don't
know... Something about them is...
*yaaaawn*...awfully familiar.

Mortals want to dream all the time,
even when they're awake... I can
understand that feeling...

Mmrgh... Hello? Oh, umm... I forgot
what $Nf said.
Yay! ...Now I can get back to my nap.
*yaaaaaawn*

Mmrgh... Having trouble
getting to sleep...
Huh? ...You woke me up for that?

*yawn* ...I'm Mirabilis. If you don't
mind, I'd like to rest just a bit more...

A long time ago, when you had just
been born, you were the cutest little
baby... You don't remember, do you?$k$pSleeping is what babies do, day...
*yaaaawn*...and at night too...$k$pBut because they sleep so much,
they need someone to watch over
them...like their mother or father.$k$pWhen I sleep here now, I feel like
I have you as the one who looks
after me while I sleep...$k$pAnd knowing... Having you there...
helps me...*yaaaawn*...sleep.
Just like a...$k$pZzzz...
それぇ
ふわぁ
ふぇぇ
Ow ow...
Hey... Why...
I'm trying to sleep...
Light's out!
Need a nap!
Now I can sleep...
*sleepy giggle*
*snoring softly, soft startle awake, back to sleep*
Mmm... How lovely...
Oh...me? I'm the ljósálfr of the—*sudden yawn*...of day...dreams...*gentle snore*
Mm-yaah! Aww... I was almost asleep...
You work so much... Aren't you exhausted?
...Mmrgh... Mother... Father...
With you near, I always rest easy...
Aw... But I... *sigh*
Mm... Sun's up!
So far...
